import {BrowserRouter, Link, Routes, Route} from "react-router-dom"
import Home from "./Pages/Home/Home"
import Research from "./Pages/Research/Research"

function App(){
    return(
        <BrowserRouter>
            <Routes>
                <Route exact path="/">
                    <Home />
                </Route>
                <Route path="/Research">
                    <Research />
                </Route>
            </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default App
